{"version":"0.9","description":"Vulmap 是一款 web 漏洞扫描和验证工具, 可对 webapps 进行漏洞扫描, 并且具备漏洞验证功能","notes":["【工具类型】: 安全测试工具","【主要功能】: Web漏洞扫描与验证工具，支持多种漏洞类型的检测和验证","【适用场景】: Web安全测试、漏洞挖掘、渗透测试","【技术特点】: Python开发，命令行工具，支持POC验证"],"homepage":"https://github.com/zhzyker/vulmap","license":"unknow","suggest":{"python":["miniconda3"]},"url":"https://github.com/zhzyker/vulmap/archive/refs/tags/v0.9.zip","hash":"0d88f770e1e39cdcf26635ee3f3f00a352c667c8aadc678ff7070bb19f313c7c","pre_install":["Set-Content \"$dir\\vulmap.bat\" '@pushd %~dp0","@call activate python3env","@python \"vulmap.py\" %*","@popd' -Encoding Ascii"],"post_install":["Move-Item -Path \"$dir\\vulmap-$version\\*\" -Destination \"$dir\\\"","Remove-Item \"$dir\\vulmap-$version\" -Force -Recurse","& cmd /c \"call activate python3env && pip install -r $dir\\requirements.txt\""],"bin":"vulmap.bat","checkver":"github","autoupdate":{"url":"https://github.com/zhzyker/vulmap/archive/refs/tags/v$version.zip"},"from":"https://github.com/bright-angel/scoop-bucket"}
